      <element xsi:type="archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel" name="03.05 AI Meta-model (Data Model)" id="id-f8c92984261e437fb988b3c740ea94f4">
        <documentation>Source: AI-BOK v1.0, Module 3, sectie 3.2, p.190</documentation>
        <property key="dct:source" value="AI-BOK v1.0, Module 3, sectie 3.2, p.190"/>
        <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-1b368f0a8e9f488d838f3bb501ce273c">
          <content>Author: Jan Willem van Veen
Modified: 2026-04-02
Source: AI-BOK v1.0, Module 3, sectie 3.2, p.190

Meta-model of the AI-BOK: the core entities (AI System, Model, Agent, Dataset, Knowledge Source) and their interrelationships.</content>
          <bounds x="0" y="0" width="380" height="148"/>
