        <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-91142130bff04dc5bb3bb0a00928cc0d">
          <content>Author: Jan Willem van Veen
Modified: 2026-04-02
Source: AI-BOK v1.0, Module 3, sectie 3.3, p.138

Governance integration patterns: how AI-BOK integrates with TOGAF, DAMA DMBOK, COBIT and GDPR.</content>
